{
  "stem": "5970.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I told you before, I lost all the members of my family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I lost contact with them, in any case.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father, as I mentioned before, was killed by the guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was beaten.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother was sent to another camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my little sister was sent away with all the children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one morning they were rounded up, and they were sent away to-- to Auschwitz, to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, if you remember in the film there was a scene where they were putting all the children onto that truck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they concentrated, obviously, on the children that belonged to the people that worked for Schindler.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The rest of the children were put onto that truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a-- a mad scene when-- when that truck left, because we were all standing on the-- on the square.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody was being counted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- they had loudspeakers with German music playing lively tunes all the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All the mothers were screaming and crying, and there the children were being led away in that-- in that truck.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And by that time, we knew that they didn't stand a chance, that this was the last time we were-- we were going to see them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my little sister was on one of-- was on that truck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They all went straight to Auschwitz, and they were all sent to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And after that, I was chosen to work for the SS women and-- as their maid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, that was also an experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I-- they lived in-- in a house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were five of them, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was this-- the same one that was in-- in Majdanek, this Else Erlich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She was in charge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She was the officer.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
